{"tid":1694391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"ifc快閃抗議警暴","createTime":"2019-11-05T06:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T06:43:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0f0a2bca8094fbd32f3984175a5d4528b5543f29","tid":1694391,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191105/DZD75TTU66LGJAHQLAM7PX7ZC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191105%2FDZD75TTU66LGJAHQLAM7PX7ZC4%2F&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=52a0d1d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191105%2FDZD75TTU66LGJAHQLAM7PX7ZC4%2F&h=4f05bec3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191105/DZD75TTU66LGJAHQLAM7PX7ZC4/</a><br />\n<br />\nifc快閃抗議警暴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】防暴警察前晚強闖多個商場驅散和平示威者造成大混亂及多人受傷，事件令巿民無比心痛，約100名中環上班族昨日趁午飯時間，在ifc商場參與快閃行動，抗議警方濫暴，同時為反送中運動傷者祈禱，祝願他們早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：200學生包圍 史維：倘證警礙救援將譴責<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/Di1AuWEZogfB3AkrzadVAVRoXbI=/802x506/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/36MC2T5BNLG3WO6OBXOQDTW4LA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FDi1AuWEZogfB3AkrzadVAVRoXbI%3D%2F802x506%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F36MC2T5BNLG3WO6OBXOQDTW4LA.gif&h=1e988472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約100名中環友在ifc參與快閃行動，抗議警方濫暴。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「唔解散警隊平息唔到民怨」<br />\n<br />\n昨下午1時許，中環上班族在商場中庭站立，眾人手持文宣，地上亦放上多張文宣，指出最新發生的不幸事件詳情，寫上「魔警橫行 人神共憤」標語。眾人不斷高叫「解散警隊 刻不容緩」、「五大訴求 缺一不可」等口號，並合唱《願榮光歸香港》，同時為事件中的傷者默站祈禱。<br />\n<br />\n參加快閃行動的中環人梁先生表示，快閃是和平表達訴求，表達對警暴的不滿，指抗爭運動持續近五個月，「發展到咁樣，成立獨立調查委員會都唔夠，唔解散警隊我覺得平息唔到民怨」。ifc快閃行動約半小時結束，眾人陸續散去。其間商場保安員從旁視察，未有上前干涉。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張培生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/ubQiD26N14aHyT8alWp3ah_hkwk=/802x510/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/SZXXX334BNQLHHIZXELPQFRQZE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FubQiD26N14aHyT8alWp3ah_hkwk%3D%2F802x510%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FSZXXX334BNQLHHIZXELPQFRQZE.gif&h=a2db22fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n參與者舉起民宣為反送中運動傷者默站祈禱。<br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"6c53abf7a92f320c1d826338417537f20a831a07","tid":1694391,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUUmQwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUUmQwH.png&h=4f6d902a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約定你11月6 Sogo崇光百貨感謝祭 下午三點銅鑼灣見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691137</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}